  - Toast type:
    - id: string
    - type: 'success' | 'error' | 'info' | 'warning'
    - title: string
    - description?: string
    - duration?: number (ms)
    - action?: { label: string; onClick: () => void }
  - Loading state:
    - message?: string
    - description?: string
- API Endpoints
  - Not required for this feature; components operate entirely client-side.
